  <brief_title>Resistance Training Exercise Using the Swiss Ball in Ankylosing Spondylitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Effectiveness of Resistance Training Exercise Using the Swiss Ball in Patients With Ankylosing Spondylitis</official_title>
